name: Broken wave #3, 2019
description: While printing work for a solo show, the paper started rejecting dyes, which pooled and re-pixellated the image. This is another of my first 'failed prints'. Originating image is a handheld zoom at dusk on rising ocean swell, Kare Kare beach, Auckland. | Minted 27  - 25 + 2 'artist proofs' |	Secondary royalties: 10%. Half to an environmental charity of my choosing.
